Description: To check that the user is able to Reset the PIN through USSD using Reset PIN request.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if MSISDN is not entered in the request.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if invalid MSISDN is entered in the request.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if  mandatory field is not entered in the request.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if invalid OTP is entered in the request.
To verify that the latest OTP is considered if Initiate PIN Reset Request is hit multiple times.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if  OTP is expired.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if  security answer is incorrect.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if New PIN is entered with invalid length.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if  alphanumeric New PIN is entered in the request.
To verify that the Reset PIN  request is not processed if  New Pin and Confirm New Pin are different.
